  /* donor_donee_reason */ 'https://forum.effectivealtruism.org/posts/xzQzLoEC5mvPyJTYY/my-q1-2022-donation-to-free-migration-project#Some_background_thinking_motivating_this_donation describes reasons the donor considers the donee worth supporting: existence value as "one of the few organizations (and the only one I clearly know) that supports freedom of movement as its core mission" and its sponsorship of the Open Borders Conference. It also discusses FMP''s room for more funding.',
